programs.programDescription: Free virtual tutoring for K – 12 students in Seattle.
programs.activityDescription: K – 12 students can get free virtual tutoring from Tutor.com with a Library card or Library Link number. Tutors are available in English, Spanish, and Vietnamese, helping with subjects like Math, Writing, Science, History, AP Classes, and more.
programs.times: 2 PM - 10 PM (English and Spanish), 4 PM - 7 PM (Vietnamese)
programs.cost: Free with Library card or Library Link number
